@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

component "Gateway_ipc_binding_client\nC++" as client
component "Gateway_ipc_binding_server\nC++" as server
component "Gateway_ipc_binding_base\nC++" as base
component "Shared_memory managers\nC++" as shm
component "SOCom runtime\nC++" as runtime

note bottom of client
  Owns one outgoing message_passing
  connection and auto-sends Connect
  when ready.
end note

note bottom of server
  Accepts multiple incoming
  message_passing connections.
end note

note bottom of base
  Shared bridge logic for service discovery,
  per-service connection state,
  and event forwarding.
end note

note bottom of shm
  Create one writable shared-memory pool
  per service instance and open peer pools
  read-only.
end note

note bottom of runtime
  Local service bridge registration plus
  client/server connector creation.
end note

client --> server : Connect / control messages
client --> base : Delegates protocol handling to
server --> base : Delegates protocol handling to
base --> shm : Allocates and opens payload memory
base --> runtime : Registers bridge and creates connectors
@enduml
